  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"Lover\" is a <i>Chinese dreamcore, psychological and survival horror game with multiple endings</i>. You play as a student who has returned from the \"<i>Lover Internet Addiction Treatment School</i>\".</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/edc06df8048bc6417ad2234f38d0f97d.avif?t=1757000340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras_big/edc06df8048bc6417ad2234f38d0f97d.avif?t=1757000340 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > After enduring <strong>mental torment</strong>, you discover the truth about \"<strong>Lover</strong>\" and yourself on <strong>an ordinary day......</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/3fc128fbd9f2b0179aad08a112725f7a.avif?t=1757000340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras_big/3fc128fbd9f2b0179aad08a112725f7a.avif?t=1757000340 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"Lover\" was developed independently by a single person over six months. The initial concept was simply \"to create a horror experience about an internet addiction treatment school through visuals and gameplay mechanics,\"<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/90d95dbf36839eb1b1930fef80fd0f76.poster.avif?t=1757000340\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/90d95dbf36839eb1b1930fef80fd0f76.webm?t=1757000340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/90d95dbf36839eb1b1930fef80fd0f76.mp4?t=1757000340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>which gradually evolved with additional elements to become the current independent horror game \"Lover.\"</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Open this door,</strong> welcome home... or, welcome to school...... A dream? Or is it your own unfathomable mental illness?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/2711a45c2e8c587ed0f1624502d194bc.avif?t=1757000340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras_big/2711a45c2e8c587ed0f1624502d194bc.avif?t=1757000340 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple endings—Multiple branches—Path choices</strong> <strong>In \"Lover,\" players can achieve up to 3 <i>different \"special\"</i> endings, </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>gradually uncovering the truth through multiple narrative paths, or... falling into the vortex of other worlds......</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/7a5f2112759994d5f9a53b1db9347d42.avif?t=1757000340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras_big/7a5f2112759994d5f9a53b1db9347d42.avif?t=1757000340 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense chase sequences, moderately challenging puzzles, and...</strong> <strong>A Sanity System—</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/e356c61c0aca4b4116bee19730a6419c.avif?t=1757000340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras_big/e356c61c0aca4b4116bee19730a6419c.avif?t=1757000340 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome home...... And, are you the next one to come here, to explore the truth?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BUG/Game content reviews <a href=\"mailto:email：mangolotis1@gmail.com\">email：mangolotis1@gmail.com</a></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"Lover\" is a <i>Chinese dreamcore, psychological and survival horror game with multiple endings</i>. You play as a student who has returned from the \"<i>Lover Internet Addiction Treatment School</i>\".</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/edc06df8048bc6417ad2234f38d0f97d.avif?t=1757000340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras_big/edc06df8048bc6417ad2234f38d0f97d.avif?t=1757000340 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > After enduring <strong>mental torment</strong>, you discover the truth about \"<strong>Lover</strong>\" and yourself on <strong>an ordinary day......</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/3fc128fbd9f2b0179aad08a112725f7a.avif?t=1757000340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras_big/3fc128fbd9f2b0179aad08a112725f7a.avif?t=1757000340 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"Lover\" was developed independently by a single person over six months. The initial concept was simply \"to create a horror experience about an internet addiction treatment school through visuals and gameplay mechanics,\"<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/90d95dbf36839eb1b1930fef80fd0f76.poster.avif?t=1757000340\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/90d95dbf36839eb1b1930fef80fd0f76.webm?t=1757000340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/90d95dbf36839eb1b1930fef80fd0f76.mp4?t=1757000340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>which gradually evolved with additional elements to become the current independent horror game \"Lover.\"</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Open this door,</strong> welcome home... or, welcome to school...... A dream? Or is it your own unfathomable mental illness?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/2711a45c2e8c587ed0f1624502d194bc.avif?t=1757000340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras_big/2711a45c2e8c587ed0f1624502d194bc.avif?t=1757000340 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple endings—Multiple branches—Path choices</strong> <strong>In \"Lover,\" players can achieve up to 3 <i>different \"special\"</i> endings, </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>gradually uncovering the truth through multiple narrative paths, or... falling into the vortex of other worlds......</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/7a5f2112759994d5f9a53b1db9347d42.avif?t=1757000340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras_big/7a5f2112759994d5f9a53b1db9347d42.avif?t=1757000340 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense chase sequences, moderately challenging puzzles, and...</strong> <strong>A Sanity System—</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3527750/extras/e356c61c0aca4b4116bee19730a6419c.avif?t=1757000340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st